OPAL (Object Oriented Parallel Accelerator Library) 

A fusion of MAD9, CLASSIC (V3.3.1 -> 4.0) MAD9p 
with the help of IPPL.

Effort started 5/12/2006 by Andreas Adelmann (PSI)


Needs: 

	IPPL
	OPAL_ROOT environment variable set

Merlin00 Modules:  1) sge/n1ge6            2) defaultenvironment   3) root/root-5.16.00    4) hdf5/hdf5-1.6.5      5) mpi/mpich2-1.0.3


Build: 

Goto opal-Build and edit make.all.sh accordingly. Then execute make.all.sh, good luck


Andreas Adelmann
